OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1775650289
OL,3,CPolice search for two men as
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues into fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FHe was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,8,FOfficers believe that he was known to
OL,9,Fhis attackers.
OL,11,FNow detectives would like to speak to
OL,12,FKieron Barnes and Tobias Agbaje who
OL,13,Fthey say may have information that
OL,14,Fcould assist the investigation.
OL,16,FThey are believed to have links to
OL,17,FHerne Bay, Whitstable, Canterbury,
OL,18,FSittingbourne, Ramsgate and London.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
